title: School Bus Converted RV, Office Room, Deck, and Huge yard
posting_body: ['Magical School Bus Experience.', 'Available Mid August', 'Ever stayed in a Skoolie?!', '(A school bus converted RV).', 'This is the perfect way to experience on-the-road, tiny home living (except not that tiny, read on).', 'Our Skoolie has: a queen and a twin bed, full bath, kitchen with a full size fridge, and a couch.', " There's AC, heat, and wifi.", " You have a place to hang your clothes and storage to put away under both beds and back of the bus 'garage'.", " There's also a deck and a yard for kids to run around.", 'The bus, the deck, and a huge yard are all yours to enjoy.', 'The  has a separate entrance and parking.', 'Bus is built as an RV for the road; therefore the water heater will stay hot for a  minute shower and will take  minutes to reheat.', " There's Roku so you can stream your hulu/netflix/disney.", 'Bus has  200sqft of livable space.', 'Comes with AC, fan, smoke alarm, lock, and lots of lights (4 windows).', 'Additional fees for couples and kid.', 'Refundable security deposit will be same as what your rent is (depending on # of people)', "No dogs but cat's allow in the tiny room, not RV.", ' $400 non-refundable pet deposit.', '3 month minimum and month to month thereafter.', 'We will teach you how to empty the black tank (easy 2 step process) if you never live in an RV before.', 'We will screen tenants on the phone first before we schedule a viewing.', ' You must make 3x/rent and no criminal background or evictions.', "We have a chicken run on our side but you won't smell a thing.", ' They are specialty chickens that does crow but not very loudly.', " With our window unit on we can't hardly hear them.", 'Across from the Blanco River and 2 min drive to Walmart off Hopkin.', ' 5mins from campus and downtown.', 'Me and my wife works from home, one kid, and 2 small dogs.', "They don't make a lot noise."]

title: House for Rent Near San Marcos!
map_address: 498 Deta Crst near Living Reef Dr
posting_body: ['Just a short drive from the San Marcos Premium Outlets, grocery, schools, shopping centers and gas stations!', "This light and airy home has plenty of space in it's living and dining areas perfect for putting up a large screen tv, sectional couches, as well as a dining table.", "Upon walking in you'll notice the elegant white tile all throughout the first floor, a large carpeted staircase and a simple half bath.", "As you keep walking you'll enter the kitchen that has it's light finishes, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.", 'The primary bed/bath is also located on the first floor past the kitchen.', "In the primary bedroom is an entry way to the master bath, here you'll see a quartz countertop dual vanity, and walk in shower as well as a spacious walk in closet.", 'Towards the back of the home is a back door that leads to a private, fully fenced, and luscious green yard.', 'Upstairs is where the second living space is located along with the second and third bedrooms and second bath.', 'The second bath includes a tub and quartz counters, while the upstairs bedrooms hold great space and bright sunlight.', 'The laundry and pantry area can be found near the garage entry way.', "Contact me directly if you'd like to learn more!"]

title: 3B/2B 1,500 sq ft
posting_body: ["Don't miss this brand new home for lease in the master planned community called Trace in San Marcos!", 'Enjoy low utility bills with this energy efficient home.', 'The fabulous floorplan is open and bright with 9 ft ceilings & beautiful wood look tile flooring throughout the main living area and kitchen.', 'The sizeable kitchen has an island for extra storage and workspace as well as an eat-in dining area perfect for fun gatherings.', 'The modern white cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances including refrigerator will not disappoint.', 'Private primary bedroom with en-suite bath including a dual vanity, walk-in shower and huge closet.', 'A sprinkler system, 2 car garage and a large covered front porch and covered patio add to the function and charm.', 'Trace offers a fantastic pool and playground, community elementary school and lots of bike and walking paths.', 'Close to IH35 for an easy commute to Austin or San Antonio.', 'Texas State University and the San Marcos Outlet Mall very close by.', 'Lots of other shopping, restaurants, hospitals and toll roads just a short drive away.', "For more details, text '208 Rollingwood' to", 'show contact info', '.', ' Listing offered by Realty Austin']
